quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,woh ( khuda ) jis ke haath mein badshahi hai barri barket wala hai. aur woh har cheez par Qadir hai
  67,2,isi ne mout aur zindagi ko pedakiya taakay tumhari azmaish kere ke tum mein kon achay amal karta hai. aur woh zabardast ( aur ) bakhsnay wala hai
  67,3,is ne saat aasman oopar taley banaye. ( ae dekhnay walay )kiya to ( khuda ) rehman ki aafrinash mein kuch nuqs daikhta hai? zara aankhh utha kar dekh bhala tujh ko ( aasman mein ) koi shagaaf nazar aata hai ?
  67,4,"phir do baara ( sah baara ) nazar kar, to nazar ( har baar ) tairay paas nakaam aur thak kar lout aeye gi"
  67,5,aur hum ne qareeb ke aasman ko ( taron ke ) charaghoon se zeenat di. aur un ko shetan ke maarny ka aala banaya aur un ke liye dehakti aag ka azaab tayyar kar rakha hai
  67,6,aur jin logon ne apne perwar-digaar se inkaarkiya un ke liye jahannum ka azaab hai. aur woh bura thikana hai
  67,7,jab woh is mein daaley jayen ge to is ka cheekhna chalana sunen ge aur woh josh maar rahi hogi
  67,8,goya maaray josh ke phatt parre gi. jab is mein un ki koi jamaat daali jaye gi to dozakh ke Darogha un se poucheen ge ke tumahray paas koi hadaayat karne wala nahi aaya tha ?
  67,9,woh kahin ge kyun nahi zaroor hadaayat karne wala aaya tha lekin hum ne is ko jhutla diya aur kaha ke khuda ne to koi cheez nazil hi nahi ki. tum to barri ghalti mein ( parre hue ) ho
  67,10,aur kahin ge agar hum suntay ya samajte hotay to dozokhiyo+A5362 mein nah hotay
  67,11,pas woh apne gunah ka iqraar karlen ge. so dozakhiyon ke liye ( rehmat khuda se ) daur hi hai
  67,12,( aur ) jo log ban dekhe apne perwar-digaar se drtay hain un ke liye bakhshish aur ajar azeem hai
